Reverse engineering toolkit for backporting Windows NT4 ScsiPort miniport drivers and NT5 (2000/XP) WDM kernel drivers to Windows 9x. Corrects LE binary headers, deploys to FAT32 disk images, provides a WDM compatibility layer for NT5 driver stacks, and includes diagnostic tools for VxD analysis. Proof of concept: NEC ATAPI miniport on Windows 98 SE.
